title: League Pun
body:
Went into an aram lobby, and someone had Nunu, but didn't want him. They offered to swap, and this happened:

GoldMedal: nunu anyone?
Faithful Puppy: nu thanks
GoldMedal: wow
GoldMedal: impressive
Faithful Puppy: thank you
Kozilek Eldrazi: best league pun ever

You are all welcome.
